extraordinary in itself.

00:00:32.350 --> 00:00:34.940
It was about mind
and brain, and it was

00:00:34.940 --> 00:00:37.930
all about what makes us humans.

00:00:37.930 --> 00:00:42.000
This lecture series now on
cosmology is what makes us.

00:00:42.000 --> 00:00:44.860
So I hope you enjoy it.

00:00:44.860 --> 00:00:48.190
Today's speaker I am really
proud of introducing,

00:00:48.190 --> 00:00:51.350
Chris Impey though many
of you may know him.

00:00:51.350 --> 00:00:53.670
Before I introduce
Chris, of course

00:00:53.670 --> 00:00:58.280
I think we have to recognize
again those folks that

00:00:58.280 --> 00:01:01.630
make it free for the rest of
us, and those are the sponsors

00:01:01.630 --> 00:01:02.730
of the lecture series.

00:01:02.730 --> 00:01:05.840
