00:52:15.430 --> 00:52:18.930
I'm barely going to mention--
and talk about where

00:52:18.930 --> 00:52:20.206
the limit of our knowledge is.

00:52:20.206 --> 00:52:21.830
Because it's still
an exciting subject,

00:52:21.830 --> 00:52:23.996
it's not like everything
is written in the textbook.

00:52:23.996 --> 00:52:26.180
When you get to the first
fraction of a second,

00:52:26.180 --> 00:52:28.470
you recognize unity
in nature symbolized

00:52:28.470 --> 00:52:31.090
by the ouroboros, an
ancient symbol found

00:52:31.090 --> 00:52:34.390
in almost all human cultures,
the snake that eats its tail.

00:52:34.390 --> 00:52:37.300
And it represents the fact
that over these 45 orders

00:52:37.300 --> 00:52:40.040
of magnitude of
scale, our best placed

00:52:40.040 --> 00:52:42.920
to test the fundamental
theories of nature, of particles

00:52:42.920 --> 00:52:45.890
and atoms at the very
high temperatures

00:52:45.890 --> 00:52:47.120
is the Big Bang itself.

00:52:47.120 --> 00:52:49.990
No batter, no other.

00:52:49.990 --> 00:52:53.160
And we can zoom over those
45 orders of magnitude

00:52:53.160 --> 00:52:54.580
from the largest
structures we see

00:52:54.580 --> 00:52:57.010
into the universe to the
quarks at the heart of an atom.

00:52:57.010 --> 00:53:00.388
Here done two seconds
for every power of 10.

